  "title": "Horticulturist/Landscape Architect with horticultural experience",
  "description": "<p>Description on duties<br>\n1.1     Formulate landscape design concepts<br>\n1.2     Prepare presentation drawings<br>\n1.3     Prepare detailed designs and planting plans for tender<br>\n1.4     Supervision of landscape site work.</p>\n<p>Qualifications<br>\n1.1     Degree in Landscape Architecture and have at least 3 years of relevant working experience in landscaping<br>\n1.2     Registration with Singapore Institute of Landscape Architects is an advantage<br>\n1.3     Ideally able to use software tools such as AutoCAD / 3D computer rendering (lumion/enscape/vray) / Photoshop / Sketch-up / Revit</p>\n<p>1.4  Knowledge of plants in tropical and temperate climate is essential</p>\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:hr@woha.net\">hr@woha.net</a></p>",
